          "activation_name": "Tongue Twister",
          "effect": "You fully unfurl the sling\u2019s tongue to grab hold of a creature within 20 feet, and attempt to move them. Attempt an Athletics check against the creature\u2019s Fortitude DC. On a success, you can move the creature up to 15 feet into any space within 20 feet of you. If you target a willing ally with this ability, you automatically succeed at the Athletics check.",
